---
import ConditionPage from '../../components/ConditionPage.astro';
---
<ConditionPage
	title="Treatment in Clapham"
	highlight="Foot Pain"
	heroSubtitle="Foot pain can affect everything, from standing comfortably day-to-day to walking, running and competing."
	breadcrumb="Foot Pain"
	seoTitle="Foot Pain Treatment in Clapham"
	seoDescription="Expert foot pain treatment in Clapham. Our combined podiatry and physiotherapy team assess load, footwear and gait to get you walking, running and competing pain free."
	introImage="/condition/foot-pain/intro.jpg"
	whoImage="/condition/foot-pain/who.jpg"
	intro={[
		"At Balance Performance Physiotherapy, we examine what's causing your symptoms rather than just addressing where the pain is. We consider factors like load, footwear and walking patterns to help you return to the activities you love with less pain and more confidence.",
	]}
	symptomsHeading="When to get your foot"
	symptomsHighlight="checked"
	symptomsList={[
		"Heel pain, especially with first steps in the morning",
		"Pain or stiffness in the Achilles tendon",
		"Pain through the arch or top of the foot",
		"Burning or discomfort in the ball of the foot",
		"Numbness or tingling in the toes",
		"Repeated ankle sprains or instability",
	]}
	treatmentHeading="How we treat"
	treatmentHighlight="foot pain"
	treatmentIntro="We combine podiatry and physiotherapy to give you the best results. Treatment may include:"
	treatmentList={[
		"Podiatry assessment of foot structure and mechanics",
		"Physiotherapy to improve strength and movement",
		"Tailored exercise programmes",
		"Gait analysis to assess walking or running patterns",
		"Footwear and training advice",
		"Shockwave therapy where appropriate",
		"Diagnostic ultrasound for deeper investigation",
	]}
	whoHeading="Who we"
	whoHighlight="help"
	whoList={[
		"Runners and sports participants managing overload injuries",
		"People with persistent heel or arch pain",
		"Children and teenagers with developing foot mechanics or dropped arches",
		"Bunion cases",
		"Post-surgery rehabilitation patients",
		"Seniors managing stiffness or arthritis",
	]}
	faqs={[
		{ q: "Do I need to see a podiatrist or a physio?", a: "Both can help, at Balance we work together for optimal outcomes." },
		{ q: "Do I need orthotics?", a: "Not always. Assessment determines if they're appropriate alongside strength and movement work." },
		{ q: "Can you treat plantar fasciitis?", a: "Yes. using taping, exercises, load management, and shockwave therapy where needed." },
		{ q: "What is gait analysis?", a: "Assessment of walking or running patterns to identify movement patterns linked to pain." },
		{ q: "Should I bring my shoes?", a: "Yes. especially frequently worn or training shoes." },
	]}
/>
